        <p>Noted complications in the literature include:<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="article-35895.r1">[1]</xref><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="article-35895.r6">[6]</xref><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="article-35895.r7">[7]</xref><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="article-35895.r8">[8]</xref><xref ref-type="bibr" rid="article-35895.r17">[17]</xref></p>
